<b>H&amp;M</b> is rapidly expanding its teams in sales, operations, and management at <b>12 different locations in Metro New York City</b>. If you have a can-do attitude and are ready for a rewarding career at one of the world's largest fashion retailers, there is an opportunity for you. <br>
<br>
<b> Click on the following link to apply to work at H&amp;M:</b>
<a href="https://jobs.apploi.com/profile/hm?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=jobboard&amp;utm_campaign=hm-profile" rel="nofollow">Apply Here</a><br>
<br>
A good opportunity is hard to find. And a career at H&amp;M is one of them. As one of the world's fastest growing fashion retailers, H&amp;M boasts as many career opportunities as there are shirt colors on their shelves. If the idea of making the fashion world go round by delivering incredible customer service sounds great to you, don't wait -- take a look and apply for a career with H&amp;M today. <br>
<br>
Looking for candidates who worked in Customer Service, Retail Sales Associates and Store Manager, Assistant Managers, Stock Associates, Retail Operations, Merchandizing, Clerks, Cashiers, Warehouse workers, and product demonstrators positions. It only takes 2 minutes to apply. <br> <br> <b>Part-time and full-time jobs available. Great for students looking for seasonal jobs and flexible hours. Night and weekend shifts available.<br></b>    </section>

<ul class="notices">
            <li>Principals only. Recruiters, please don't contact this job poster.</li>
            <li>do NOT contact us with unsolicited services or offers</li>
</ul>

